title: MNAs call on prime minister
content:
ISLAMABAD. Dec 21 (APP): Members of the National Assembly from different constituencies called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here on Wednesday.
The parliamentarians who met the prime minister included Hamid Hameed, Rana Mubashir Iqbal and Rao Muhammad Ajmal.
During the meeting, they discussed matters of mutual interest.
